  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will be conducted, in cross-over with a time interval of at least 2 days between 2
      treatment periods. Patients will be randomized into 2 groups According to the order of the
      randomization, patients will bear the JewelPump for 5 days, followed by a period of 5 days of
      treatment with their usual pumps.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The JewelPump (Debiotech) will be compared to the conventional pumps. Patients will treated
      with the JewelPump during 5 days, and with their usual pump during 5 other days.

      The study will be conduct with 15 patients at the following investigation centers : Corbeil
      Hospital, CHU of Strasbourg, and CHRU of Marseille.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
